#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:797
msgid "Ready-made blocklists for ads and harmful sites. Matching traffic will be blocked. Choose the ones you want to use, or leave this empty."
msgstr "预置的拦截列表，用于广告和有害网站。匹配的流量将被拦截。选择您想要使用的，或者留空。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:837
